      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_30_liras_trial_the_unfinished_forge_005",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "Lira?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_30_liras_trial_the_unfinished_forge_006",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "It had his face. The Machine. It looked like Cael and",
        "it asked me to fix it."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_30_liras_trial_the_unfinished_forge_007",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "What did you do?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": [
        {
          "who": "sable",
          "anim": "head_down",
          "when": "before_line_0"
        }
      ],
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_30_liras_trial_the_unfinished_forge_008",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "I took it apart. Because that's what you do with",
        "something that can't be fixed. You learn from it and you build",
        "something else."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_30_liras_trial_the_unfinished_forge_009",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "That's new."
